overview: Team K-DOJO (Yoshiaki Yago & MIYAWAKI) ascend through the ranks, but at the expense of Lancelot! Larry Sweeney looks to teach a lesson to his one-time bodyguard, Mana! The main event relevos atomicos match features Mike Quackenbush, Jigsaw, Shane Storm & Milano Collection AT vs. The Kings of Wrestling in the main event!
title: Chikara: Aniversario Delta
